        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Pell Grant Cost of Tuition Adjustment Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends title IV (Student Assistance) of the Higher Education Act of 1965 to set the maximum Pell Grant at a specified amount, increased for inflation each year, plus any additional amount specified in the last enacted appropriation Act.</p>]]></text>
